Line3.103673: I must return to Zarbinzet. I shall tell the other Zakarum of Carthas and the paladins who gave their lives to contain Mephisto's corruption.
Line8.103673: May the Light guide your way.
Line1.103673: Yes, (deep breath) I believe so. The paladins are finally at peace. I could not have done this alone. The Light shines bright within you.
VoiceDir1.103673: Tired, but still full of spirit.
